{"tid":1081027,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ufotable擬似逃稅","createTime":"2019-03-28T04:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T06:47:59.000Z","uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff37a6144832a28bf1cebf9b2bb696a8fea09ecb","tid":1081027,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"曾製作《Fate/stay night》、《空之境界》等作品的知名動畫公司ufotable被爆涉嫌在動漫週邊銷售上逃稅，正遭到日本國稅局調查。<br />\n<br />\n594cc12141295.jpg1234.jpg<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒《週刊文春》透露，日本國稅局以涉嫌逃稅為由，於3月12日派人搜查ufotable位於高圓寺和德島咖啡廳、下井草的東京工作室，而高円寺更有近30進入調查。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，ufotable的社長曾到部份售賣週邊的店舖，親自收取自家商品銷售所得的盈利，而非直接存入銀行戶口，並在帳目上隱藏這方面所得的金錢。<br />\n<br />\n有前國稅局調查官認為事件會花約1年時間調查，有可能會起訴或拘捕有關人士。<br />\n<br />\nDSC_1234.jpg<br />\n<br />\n面對傳媒提問，國稅局回應說不會回答個別案件。但有傳ufotable社長近藤光已承認指控。而ufotable則叫傳媒直接向近藤光查詢，但後者截稿前都未有回應。 <br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/16227876/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.livedoor.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F16227876%2F&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AL%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=d6259600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/16227876/</a><br />\n<br />\n週刊文春:fate hf 劇場版制作動畫公司ufotable擬似有逃稅<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1080844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1080844</a>"},{"pid":"6e48a9302a1f9d1edeba8615f85a27c9aef64459","tid":1081027,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"套hf 已經就執咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...<br />\nBgm勁濃厚 空境<br />\n第2集 黑saber同巴叔係到玩粉塵煙花燈光夜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母比返deen做好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37744c4ff6f696a6b049bbe69c21e170a20b72ff","tid":1081027,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm